#

Hearty Pork and Bean Chili

75 min
$10.5
400 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 6

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freehigh-protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

comfort foodeasyhearty

Description

A warm and filling chili made with tender pork and hearty beans, perfect for a cozy meal.

Ingredients

  • ground pork: 1 pound
  • canned kidney beans: 2 cans
  • canned black beans: 1 can
  • canned diced tomatoes: 1 can
  • onion: 1 medium, chopped
  • bell pepper: 1 medium, chopped
  • garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • chicken broth: 2 cups
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • chili powder: 2 tablespoons
  • cumin: 1 tablespoon
  • paprika: 1 teaspoon
